  "body": "### Description\nCreate a sample implementation for the smart contract based validator selection.\nThis will be based on https://docs.google.com/document/d/1100I7Dm36D-mP9ZUpjfxxKtuJ2uhFpp3DkgjH8AdFR0/edit#\n\n- Create the interface smart contract \n- Create the sample implementation based on an allow list (see document above)\n    - To make the smart contract upgradeable use the OpenZeppelin transparent upgradeable proxy contract (https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/tree/master/contracts/proxy/transparent)\n    - Consider using one of the OpenZeppelin access contracts (Ownable, AccessControl, AccessControlEnumerable) \n- testing - see permissioning SC repo for JS testing\n\n",
